text: Khaled Al Muqaitib (; born 3 June 1992) is a Saudi professional footballer who plays for Al-Fayha as a goalkeeper. ==Career== Al Muqaitib started his career with Al-Raed where he was promoted from the youth team to the first team in 2014 .He played his first match against Al-Ahli on April 30, 2017 . left Al- Raed and signed with Al-Qaisumah on a one-year loan on July 11, 2018 . left Al-Raed and signed with Al-Fayha in October 17, 2020. ==References== == External links == * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Saudi Arabian footballers Category:Al-Raed FC players Category:Al-Qaisumah FC players Category:Al-Fayha FC players Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Saudi Professional League players Category:Prince Mohammad bin Salman League players
